      var addJquery = document.createElement("script")
      addJquery.src  = "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7/jquery.min.js"
      addJquery.onload = function() {
        var container  = document.getElementById("curalate-fan-reel-wrapper")

          addCuralate()
        }
      }
      document.body.appendChild(addJquery)
